title: Number of the Beast
tags: 2014 Amiga ChipMetal cover Heavy IronMaiden Metal Musicdisk
info:
One of my two contributions for the Iron Maiden tribute chipmusicdisk released by Up-Rough, Titan and Insane at Compusphere 2014.

Iron Maiden has always been one of my favourite bands, but this song was painful to cover as I aimed as getting it as close as i could to the original. It took a few hours :)
